---
title: Sichuan-Glazed Popcorn Chicken Tacos with Creamy Slaw
description: Taco night has been transformed! Crispy bites of chicken have been coated in a sticky Sichuan paste for bags of flavour, before being nestled inside warm tortillas with a creamy and tangy slaw. It’s another taco-tastic dinner!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/672d2f96ba08659748631f9d-b381a089.jpeg
